@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_orhvyj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.sin(v1 + 0.56) - (v0 + 0.94 * tmp + 0.71)))
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.33)) - ((v0 + 0.02 / v0 + 0.13) / wp.sin(tmp + 0.20)))
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.exp(v1 + 0.81) * 0.70))
    v2 = 0.36
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
